column1: # Note: In the following rows commas have been replaced with semicolons to work better with r
# In order to determine H3K9me2 marked genes; we employed published H3K9me2 ChIP-seq dataset SRX495107 (Gerstein et al.; 2010)
# and performed peak calling analysis using MACS (Lupien et al.; 2008). We then defined H3K9me2 marked genes as genes for which
# a significant H3K9me2 peak (FDR Qvalue < 0.1) overlaps the 1;000 bp centered around their TSS.
